  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Starting at 9th level, you have learned to infuriate your enemies almost subconsciously, it becoming second nature to you. You learn the <em><strong>Song of Reversal</strong></em> jutsu, if you do not know it already. If you already know <em><strong>Song of Reversal</strong></em> then you instead add another jutsu of equal rank for which you qualify for. When casting <em><strong>Song of Reversal</strong></em> you can choose to no longer spend your bonus action to maintain it, but it gains a concentration cost as normal and you cannot lose concentration of this jutsu as a result of damage.</p><p>If you target a creature currently analyzed with <em><strong>Exploit Weakness</strong></em>, they have disadvantage on the initial saving throw.</p>",
